Privacy Policy

Last updated: August 6, 2024

1. Introduction
Welcome to Aliens vs Humans! We are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our game.

2. Company Information
Developer Name: Infernus
Contact Email: ilirhdev@gmail.com

3. Information Collection
Aliens vs Humans does not collect any personal data directly from users. However, our game integrates with third-party services such as AdMob, which may collect certain information to serve personalized ads.

4. Information Usage
While we do not collect personal data, the third-party services integrated within our game may use information such as device identifiers, location, crash logs, and other information for providing ads and analytics.

5. Data Storage
Aliens vs Humans does not store personal data. Third-party services like AdMob may store data according to their privacy policies.

6. User Rights
As we do not directly collect user data, user rights to access, modify, or delete data are not applicable. However, users may refer to the privacy policies of the third-party services for managing their data rights.

7. Security
We prioritize the security of our game and use industry-standard measures to ensure your experience is safe. However, since we do not collect or store personal data, we rely on third-party services for data security.

8. Ads and Analytics
Aliens vs Humans uses AdMob to serve ads within the game. AdMob may collect and use data to provide personalized advertising experiences. You can manage your ad preferences and consent choices through your device settings or the options provided in the consent dialog.

9. Children’s Privacy
Aliens vs Humans is not directed to children under 13. We comply with the Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA) and do not knowingly collect data from children under 13.

10. Changes to Privacy Policy
Any changes to this Privacy Policy will be communicated to users by contacting us at ilirhdev@gmail.com. We recommend checking this Privacy Policy periodically for updates.

11. Acceptance of Terms
By using Aliens vs Humans, you consent to this Privacy Policy and the terms outlined within.